Here's a simple HTML and JavaScript code snippet to create a fake chatbot simulation. This code creates a chat window where the user can input messages and the chatbot responds accordingly. The chat history is displayed below the input field.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chatbot Simulation</title>
    <style>
        /* Style the chat window */
        #chat-window {
            width: 300px;
            height: 400px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 10px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        #user-input {
